# Stitch Design Fidelity — Always 1:1

When any Stitch screen ID is mentioned or a design task involves a Stitch project, **never approximate**. Follow this exact protocol every time.

## Mandatory Steps (in order)

1. **Fetch via MCP first** — call `get_screen` with the project/screen IDs before writing any code.
2. **Download both assets** — screenshot (`downloadUrl`) AND HTML code (`htmlCode.downloadUrl`) using `Invoke-WebRequest`.
3. **Read the screenshot** — use the Read tool to view the image. Visually analyse every element.
4. **Diff HTML vs current code** — identify every class, color, layout, and animation that differs.
5. **Implement 1:1** — copy exact values: colors, border-radius, opacity, animation timings, easing curves, font sizes. Do not invent or approximate.
6. **Verify the diff list is empty** before committing.

## Common Mistakes to Avoid

| ❌ Wrong (approximation) | ✅ Correct (exact Stitch) |
|---|---|
| Amber/teal glow blobs | `w-[800px] bg-white opacity-[0.02] blur-[150px]` centered blob |
| Pink active filter pill | `bg-white text-black border-white` solid white |
| Pink step icons | `bg-white border-[3px] border-[#0d0d0f]` white circle |
| Pink hash text | `color: #ffffff` plain white |
| Gradient title | `color: #ffffff` plain white uppercase |
| Separate header + input cards | Single combined `flex-col lg:flex-row` bento card |
| `position: fixed` for glow inside SPA | `position: absolute` scoped to panel |

## CSS Translation Rules (Tailwind → custom CSS)

When the project has no Tailwind, translate utility classes to raw CSS:
- `bg-[#0d0d0f]` → `background: #0d0d0f`
- `border border-white/5` → `border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05)`
- `rounded-3xl` → `border-radius: 1.5rem`
- `opacity-[0.02]` → `opacity: 0.02`
- `blur-[150px]` → `filter: blur(150px)`
- `bg-white/5` → `background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05)`
- `border-white/20` → `border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.20)`

## Animation Timings (never change these)

```
bento entrance:  0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1)
data-pulse:      2.5s linear infinite
breath-glow:     3s ease-in-out infinite
shimmer-edge:    2s infinite (on focus)
magnetic button: 0.2s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94)
mesh-float:      20s ease-in-out infinite alternate
cursor-blink:    1s step-end infinite
spring:          0.5s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1)
```
